snippet.description:
Yogi Vs Sunny Deol | Battle Of Galwan Ban By Yogi | Salman Khan Angry 😡 | Galwan Movie Trailer 

Sunny Deol’s Bold Statement Shocks Yogi! Battle of Galwan Movie Sparks Huge Controversy



The Indian film industry and the political landscape are shaken to the core! What began as a thunderous poster launch of “Battle of Galwan” has now exploded into a full-blown national controversy—pitting Bollywood heavyweight Salman Khan against Uttar Pradesh’s power-packed CM Yogi Adityanath.
In this explosive video, we peel back the layers of the “raw and unfiltered reality” that this film claims to expose. How did one rugged, war-torn image of Salman Khan ignite such a massive political firestorm? And why has Sunny Deol, the eternal symbol of cinematic patriotism, stepped forward with a roaring statement that has left everyone stunned?
From CM Yogi Adityanath’s stern warning against turning national sacrifice into box-office business, to Sunny Deol’s fearless, no-holds-barred stand for creative independence, the clash has reached boiling point. Is Battle of Galwan revealing uncomfortable truths, or is it crossing a line in the name of cinema?
Salman Khan remains silent—for now. But in a storm this big, silence speaks louder than words.
This is more than a movie controversy. This is a battle of Deshbhakti vs. Dissent, Power vs. Expression.
Watch till the end to uncover what’s really happening behind closed doors—and decide for yourself: Who is speaking the truth?
